      "level": 3,
      "text": "About the Section"
    },
    {
      "id": "n2",
      "type": "image",
      "order": 1,
      "src": "https://deutsch-pruefung.de/_next/image?url=%2Fsection-assets%2Fbear-mascot.webp&w=384&q=75",
      "alt": "Study bear mascot"
    },
    {
      "id": "n3",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 2,
      "text": "The official telc Deutsch C1 Hörverstehen section takes about 40 minutes and has 48 points. It consists of Globalverstehen (global understanding), Detailverstehen (detailed understanding), and Informationstransfer (information transfer) tasks."
    },
    {
      "id": "n4",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 3,
      "level": 4,
      "text": "Teil 1: Globalverstehen (Global Understanding)"
    },
    {
      "id": "n5",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 4,
      "text": "• Listen for the overall message, speaker stance, or central idea"
    },
    {
      "id": "n6",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 5,
      "text": "• Solve 8 Zuordnungsaufgaben"
    },
    {
      "id": "n7",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 6,
      "level": 4,
      "text": "Teil 2: Detailverstehen (Detailed Understanding)"
    },
    {
      "id": "n8",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 7,
      "text": "• Listen to a longer spoken text such as a radio interview or discussion"
    },
    {
      "id": "n9",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 8,
      "text": "• Choose the best answer from three options for each item"
    },
    {
      "id": "n10",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 9,
      "level": 4,
      "text": "Teil 3: Informationstransfer (Information Transfer)"
    },
    {
      "id": "n11",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 10,
      "text": "• Listen to one lecture, presentation, or seminar-style talk"
    },
    {
      "id": "n12",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 11,
      "text": "• Complete missing information in a handout or notes"
    },
    {
      "id": "n13",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 12,
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Teil 1 - Globalverstehen (Global Understanding)"
    },
